name: AMP-UP™ 100
description: AMP-UP™ 100 Self-Healing Primer is compatible with AMP-UP™ ACRYLIC, AMP-UP™ URETHANE, and AMP-UP™ PROSHIELD to provide a comprehensive protective coating system. AMP-UP™ 100 Self-Healing Primer can be used for indoor or outdoor applications and performs better than two-component solvent-borne primers in similar environments. In addition, AMP-UP™ 100 Self-Healing Primer comes in a one component package, is easily applied by spray, roller or brush, is easy to clean up, has low odor and low VOC and is environmentally friendly
